<header>
    <h1>NovaSolar AI</h1>
    <p>Remote-First Workplace Policy</p>
</header>

<section>
    <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
    <p>
        NovaSolar AI operates as a Remote-First organization, built on flexibility, performance, and global collaboration. 
        As an AI-driven climate technology company, we believe innovation thrives when exceptional talent is empowered — regardless of geography.
    </p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Workplace Principles</h2>

    <div class="principle">
        <h3>1. Remote by Design</h3>
        <p>Our infrastructure, workflows, and communication systems are optimized for distributed teams across time zones.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="principle">
        <h3>2. Outcome-Oriented Performance</h3>
        <p>We prioritize measurable impact over physical presence. Results, innovation, and execution define performance.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="principle">
        <h3>3. Asynchronous Collaboration</h3>
        <p>We leverage structured documentation, version control, and digital collaboration tools to ensure seamless teamwork.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="principle">
        <h3>4. Global Talent Access</h3>
        <p>We recruit top engineers, data scientists, and energy experts worldwide — without location constraints.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="principle">
        <h3>5. Security & Compliance First</h3>
        <p>All remote operations follow strict cybersecurity, data protection, and regulatory standards.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="principle">
        <h3>6. Strategic Alignment</h3>
        <p>We conduct virtual or location-based strategic sessions when required to ensure long-term alignment and R&D acceleration.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Why Remote?</h2>
    <p>
        NovaSolar AI builds autonomous intelligence for distributed solar systems. 
        Our organizational design reflects the distributed, intelligent energy future we are enabling.
    </p>
</section>

